9_0	0.375	WASHINGTON _ The heated battle over how to use projected federal budget surpluses has exposed deep rifts between the two parties, both in political and economic terms.
9_1	0.7777777777777778	It has divided Democrats and Republicans over such basic issues as whether there really is a federal budget surplus.
