9_13	0.041666666666666664	But Democrats point out that the surplus projections are based on a series of questionable premises: that the economy will avoid a protracted downturn; that unexplained surges in revenue will continue, and that the forecasting ability of budget analysts will prove far more accurate than it has in the past.
9_14	0.0	Further, the projections assume what many say is an unrealistically low level of increases in government spending.
